Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; ⚠️  RISKY - Remove Windows Security Health Service Entry
; 
; THIS FILE IS EXPERIMENTAL AND RISKY - USE WITH CAUTION
; 
; What this removes:
; - Completely deletes the SecurityHealthService registry entry
; - Removes all associated service configurations
; - May cause system instability or unexpected behavior
; 
; Why it's risky:
; - Does not gracefully disable the service, completely removes it
; - May interfere with Windows Update or system stability
; - Cannot be easily reversed without system restore
; 
; Safer alternative:
; Use Remove_SecurityComp.reg which disables the service instead of removing it
; 
; ⚠️  PROCEED ONLY IF YOU KNOW WHAT YOU'RE DOING ⚠️

[-HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\SecurityHealthService]
